## Desenvolupament

Fem el desenvolupament oportú segons la tasca assignada.

---

## Crear un **Pull Request** (**PR**)

---

<div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:2rem;">
  <div style="flex:1;">

```bash
gh pr create --base main --head <nomBranca>
```

  </div>
  <div style="flex:1;">
    <p>Creem el PR cap a <code>main</code>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

---

<div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:2rem;">
  <div style="flex:1;">

```bash
gh pr edit N --add-reviewer usuari
```

  </div>
  <div style="flex:1;">
    <p>Assignem un revisor al PR.</p>
  </div>
</div>

---

## Fer Review

```bash
gh pr review N --approve
```

```bash
gh pr review N --request-changes --body "Comentari"
```

---

## Fer Merge

```bash
gh pr merge N --delete-branch
```

---

## Veure les Issues

```bash
gh issue list
```

---

# Resultat final

**Issue → Branch → PR → Review → Merge → Done**

El Project mostra l’estat visual del treball.
